### Project API Tests

### 1. Create a new project
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Project
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectName": "Task Management System",
  "isActive": true,
  "description": "A comprehensive task management system for teams"
}

### 2. Get all projects
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Project

### 3. Get project by ID
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Project/1

### 4. Update project
PUT https://localhost:7001/api/Project/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectName": "Updated Task Management System",
  "isActive": true,
  "description": "An updated comprehensive task management system for teams"
}

### 5. Delete project (soft delete)
DELETE https://localhost:7001/api/Project/1

### 6. Create another project
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Project
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectName": "E-commerce Platform",
  "isActive": true,
  "description": "Online shopping platform with payment integration"
} 